{
  "stem": "26672.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "We always worked in twos.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "I don't remember the guy that I worked with, but he stood watch in the barrack to see if anybody going-- that particular day, luckily, he told me not to come, because he was going away on holiday, or leave, or whatever.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I managed to get into the barrack, steal his revolver, and hid it in a place wherein I thought, obviously, I'll hear when they're going to escape and I'll join with them.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I'm sure they wouldn't want me if I officially, but I thought if I turned up, then-- but unlucky for me, they-- they escaped.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But the day when they escaped, they stopped going to work, my group.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I was taken to Tschenstochau, further into another camp.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So they escaped, but I, unfortunately, ended up in a-- in another a camp, a labor camp.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And did your, is it commandant at the camp ever find-- or sergeant ever find that his pistol had been stolen?",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, yes, he did.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes, he did.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He came-- what happened was, they had parades.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He came back from his holiday, from leave, whatever, and he was in a parade.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "An officer came to inspect.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they always-- you know, you take  your weapon.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You're getting your weapon ready, and so forth.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we were standing from a distance watching in the parade ground.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And just before he came to his then, he got himself ready and started-- he looks and he's got nothing there.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So I think he was a sergeant, or whatever.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He managed to leave and go back to his place and look for it.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He didn't find it.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
